265
00:14:06.200 --> 00:14:09.800
Lulla, lulla, lullaby, lulla,lulla, lullaby.

266
00:14:09.800 --> 00:14:11.670
Never harm, nor spell nor charm,

267
00:14:11.670 --> 00:14:13.630
